Comment: White Kingdom begins its march across the mountain, stopping to rest at about the halfway point between the two kingdoms.
The Kingside Reconnaissance Team moves out of the castle area to get a closer look at reports of a White Kingdom squadron moving closer to the Black Kingdom.
While the squadron originating from d2 rests, Daxter sends c2 to accompany them.
Antony deploys a squadron next to the reconnaissance team as a precaution, since the Whites' intentions are still uncertain.
The squadron of c2 moves ahead of d2, disobeying orders to wait for them.
The reconnaissance team moves fairly close to the two White Squadrons, but any attempt at communication is ignored.
The squadron of c2 moves up, ignoring the ordeal of those from d2 being blocked by the reconnaissance team.

The Black Survey Corps are the first to spot the squadron, and assume the worst.

The squadron of c2 is destroyed and the Survey Corps get information from the reconnaissance team.
